        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/j/97f17d/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2020-04-19T17:35:02.218Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Thank you for your response and help, I entered</p>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-auto\">curl -s https://updates.signal.org/desktop/apt/keys.asc\n```and it went fine, then I entered\n</code></pre>\n<p>sudo apt-key add -</p>\n<pre data-code-wrap=\"and\"><code class=\"lang-plaintext\"></code></pre>\n<p>sudo apt-key add -  echo “deb [arch=amd64] <a href=\"https://updates.signal.org/desktop/apt\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://updates.signal.org/desktop/apt</a> xenial main”<br>\nand it sat there forever, so I am stumped<br>\nthanks again</p>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-auto\"></code></pre>",
